app.title: Generador y validador de CPF de código abierto | Tiago Porto
app.description: JS lib to generate and validate CPF (Cadastro de Pessoas Físicas) of Brazil.

header.title: CPF Generator and validator
header.libInfo: JS open-source lib to generate and validate CPF.

info.disclaimer: Lib available to assist developers in software testing, has no connection with the Brazilian Federal Revenue.
info.disclaimerValidCPF: A valid CPF does not mean that it exists nor is active. For that information, check the official website of <0>Department of Federal Revenue of Brazil</0>.
info.cpfByState: The last digit before verifiers (the last two digits), corresponds to the Brazilian state where the CPF was issued.
info.example: Example: CPF <0>XXX.XXX.XX8-XX</0>, 8 corresponds to São Paulo state.
info.stateCode1: 1. Distrito Federal, Goiás, Mato Grosso do Sul and Tocantins;
info.stateCode2: 2. Pará, Amazonas, Acre, Amapá, Rondônia and Roraima;
info.stateCode4: 4. Pernambuco, Rio Grande do Norte, Paraíba and Alagoas;
info.stateCode7: 7. Rio de Janeiro and Espírito Santo;
